INSERT INTO `destoon_company_data` VALUES('733','<p>\n        					        					        						<br><br><br><br>永柏塑胶电镀厂，是由香港永柏实业有限公司投资的中外合资企业，成立于1986年，是一间专业的ABS塑胶电镀厂。随着业务的不断发展，公司于1989年将生产线迁移至深圳市龙岗区坑梓镇沙田工业区，现拥有厂房面积8,000平方米，占地面积12,000平方米，员工人数约为350人。<br>本公司拥有现代化的厂房，两条环形全自动生产线，同时还拥有一间精密塑料、塑胶注塑无尘车间。在质量控制方面，有严格而科学的管理系统和检测手段，配备了一系列先进的质量检测设备。我司严格运行ISO9001：2000质量体系，并且在2007年5月通过了摩迪国际集团ISO14001：2004环境体系的认证。<br>本公司主要是对各种ABS,ABS+PC塑胶制品外表面进行装饰性电镀，可选择的电镀品种有：三价铬、光镍及不锈钢色等十多种颜色，并不懈致力于开发市场及环保方向新的电镀工艺（如：无镍电镀）。电镀应用范围：汽车标志及内外部装饰件，电话机、手机、家电外壳及按键，卫浴产品，数码相机装饰件等。<br>公司培养了一批专业的技术人员和管理人才，从开模到注塑及电镀为客户提供一条龙服务，我们热忱希望与世界各地商界人士和朋友建立广泛的合作关系。<br>Winpak Plastic Electroplate Factory is a professional ABS electroplating factory which was established in 1986, invested by Hong Kong Winpak Industrial Co., Ltd. Along with the needs of the growing business, the company was transferred its product line to Shatian Kenzi Longgang District Shenzhen in 1989.Now, we has a construction area of 8,000 m2, ground 12,000 m2, with 350 employees.<br>We have modern workshop, two loop automatic product line and possesses a dust-free Precision Injection workshop as well. For quality control, we follow the scientific managing system and measurement method with serial high-tech test equipments. We follow quality system of ISO9001:2000 strictly. And we have passed ISO14001:2004 environmental system certification in May 2007.<br>Winpak focuses mainly on the surface treatment of ABS&nbsp;or&nbsp;ABS+PC plastic product. We can plate trivalent bright chrome, bright nickel, stainless steel brushed+nickel, etc. We are never stopping our foot for the plating market development. So far we are succeeding in nickel free plating and more high tech & high quality product according to customer’s special requirements. <br>From Injection to electroplating, we own professional team workers; we own long years experience in plating area. We believe we can give you the best service.        				                			</p>');
